      <a href="index.html?p=1751#comment-1336"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2007-03-22T00:39:00-04:00">Thursday, March 22, 2007 at 12:39 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>How fun!  I love Pikes Place Market, and I am determined to someday do a stay in Paris like yours.  It&#8217;s one of those &#8220;to do before you die&#8221; kind of things I think &#8211; or at least it&#8217;s one of mine!  I made the &#8220;rancho la puerta&#8221; granola that I found on your recipe list the other day and I am planning to post about it &#8211; I love it!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
